Sentencas: (Pr-Nd)(1-y)SryMnO3-delta (P-NSM,y=0.2,0.25,0.3,0.35) powders made from commercial Pr-Nd mixed oxide, as well as (Pr1-x,Nd-x)(0.7)Sr0.3MnO3-delta (PN3SM, x=0, 0.5, 0.7, 1) were synthesized by a glycine-nitrate process and characterized as cathode materials for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical properties of (Pr-Nd)1-ySryMnO3-δ and (Pr1-xNdx)0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ as cathode materials for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: XRD patterns showed the powders had formed pure perovskite phase after being calcined at 800 degrees C for 2h.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical properties of (Pr-Nd)1-ySryMnO3-δ and (Pr1-xNdx)0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ as cathode materials for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: (Pr-Nd)(0.7)Sr0.3MnO3-delta (P-N3SM) achieved a high conductivity of 194 S cm(-1) at 500 degrees C and showed a good chemical stability against YSZ at 1150 degrees C.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical properties of (Pr-Nd)1-ySryMnO3-δ and (Pr1-xNdx)0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ as cathode materials for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: And the thermal expansion coefficient of P-N3SM/YSZ cathode was 11.1 x 10(-6) K-1, which well matched YSZ electrolyte film.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical properties of (Pr-Nd)1-ySryMnO3-δ and (Pr1-xNdx)0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ as cathode materials for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The tubular SOFC with P-N3SM/YSZ cathode exhibited the maximum power densities of 415, 367,327 and 282 mW cm(-2) at 850,800,750 and 700 degrees C, respectively, which indicated P-N3SM was potentially applied in SOFC for low cost.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrochemical properties of (Pr-Nd)1-ySryMnO3-δ and (Pr1-xNdx)0.7Sr0.3MnO3-δ as cathode materials for IT-SOFC
